OL,3,CCardiff Council Leader says half a
OL,4,Cdozen 20mph roads' could be reviewed
OL,5,Cin city
OL,7,F"Half a dozen" 20mph roads in Cardiff
OL,8,Fcould revert to their original speed
OL,9,Flimit, according to the Leader of
OL,10,FCardiff Council.
OL,12,FSpeaking to Catrin Haf Jones on S4C's
OL,13,FY Byd yn ei Le, Labour Councillor Huw
OL,14,FThomas said: "I can say that certainly
OL,15,Fin Cardiff's case, there will be a
OL,16,Freview. This is a policy we've been
OL,17,Fintroducing in Cardiff over a number
OL,18,Fof years.
