OL,3,CCardiff Council Leader says half a
OL,4,Cdozen 20mph roads' could be reviewed
OL,5,Cin city
OL,7,F"When the law came into place in
OL,8,FSeptember, only 24 streets in the city
OL,9,Fchanged their speed limits."
OL,11,FWhen asked whether any of these
OL,12,Fstreets will change from a 20mph
OL,13,Flimit, Huw Thomas responded: "Half a
OL,14,Fdozen, possibly."
OL,16,FWhen asked what lead him to that
OL,17,Fnumber, Mr Thomas said it was a "sniff
OL,18,Ftest."
