OL,3,CCardiff Council Leader says half a
OL,4,Cdozen 20mph roads' could be reviewed
OL,5,Cin city
OL,7,F"I think it's right we look and
OL,8,Flisten. But generally, the speed
OL,9,Flimits will stay as they are."
OL,11,FThe 20mph limit in urban and
OL,12,Fresidential areas came into force
OL,13,Facross Wales in September 2023, and
OL,14,Fhas been met with opposition in the
OL,15,FSenedd from the Welsh Conservatives. A
OL,16,Fpetition calling on the Welsh
OL,17,FGovernment to remove the law has
OL,18,Freceived nearly 500,000 signatures.
