OL,3,CCardiff Council Leader says half a
OL,4,Cdozen 20mph roads' could be reviewed
OL,5,Cin city
OL,7,FTransport Secretary Ken Skates said in
OL,8,Fresponse to a debate tabled by the
OL,9,FConservatives in the Senedd on
OL,10,FWednesday that there will be a review
OL,11,Finto 20mph zones to ensure that
OL,12,Fthey're "targeted" in areas "where
OL,13,Fchildren and the elderly are at risk."
OL,15,F"I think the change of emphasis shows
OL,16,Fhow Vaughan Gething and Ken Skates
OL,17,Fwant to be a government that listens,
OL,18,Fand that's to be welcomed," said Mr
OL,19,FThomas.
