OL,3,CCardiff Council Leader says half a
OL,4,Cdozen 20mph roads' could be reviewed
OL,5,Cin city
OL,7,F"I think the opposition has made a lot
OL,8,Fof fuss over this policy. But very
OL,9,Fsimply, what the law does is enable
OL,10,Flocal councils to have 20mph in place
OL,11,Fas a minimum.
OL,13,FHere in Cardiff, over the last eight
OL,14,Fyears of introducing 20mph in ward
OL,15,Fafter ward after ward, it was a very
OL,16,Flong process to achieve that - and the
OL,17,Fnew law says 'That's the minimum, if
OL,18,Fyou want to increase the speed, you
OL,19,Fcan do that', and you have to go
OL,20,Fthrough a long process to increase the
OL,21,Fspeed.
